    "created_at": "2012-03-23T14:16:08Z",
    "updated_at": "2012-03-23T14:16:08Z",
    "body": "I think this is too restrictive. Updating or removing the item currently being pointed at is extremely useful, and not hard to support. Forcing people to write their own update list when doing a modifying pass over a map would be an admission of defeat wrt usability.\n",
