    "created_at": "2012-03-23T14:58:00Z",
    "updated_at": "2012-03-23T14:58:00Z",
    "body": "We could allow modification to the current key, but I would be inclined to add a mapValues method instead. It is more efficient (no need to rehash) and more declarative of the intention.\n",
